Singapore
Publish Start Date
Apr 2 2014
Job Level
Experienced (Non-Manager)
|
Responsibilities:
Develop and manage distributors in Singapore.
Develop and manage OEM direct customers.
Track and follow up project sales market.
Provide technical support and training to customers and distributors.
Market analysis and competitor information.
Achieve the assigned sales volume.
Requirements:
Degree in Engineering related to fluid control, mechanism, automation or relevant discipline.
With 3 years or above sales experiences in pressure reducing regulators, preferred experiences in high pressure regulator market like Swagelok, Parker, AP Tech or Gentec.
Good understanding of products application industries like chemical, analytical, instruments, oil and gas, petrochemical or testing.
Good communication skills with training experience to distributors and end users.